            <section class="build-summary">
                <h2>Build Overview</h2>
                <p>Learn to construct this serene and intricate Japanese Pagoda. Our detailed guide breaks down every layer, from foundation to rooftop, inspired by traditional designs.</p>
                <div class="key-info">
                    <p><strong>Difficulty:</strong> Intermediate</p>
                    <p><strong>Estimated Build Time:</strong> 4-6 hours</p>
                    <p><strong>Dimensions (approx):</strong> 25W x 25L x 40H blocks</p>
                    <p><strong>Minecraft Version:</strong> Java 1.18+ / Bedrock</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="materials-list">
                <h2>Required Materials (Example)</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Dark Oak Wood: ~8 Stacks</li>
                    <li>Spruce Wood Planks: ~6 Stacks</li>
                    <li>Stone Bricks: ~10 Stacks</li>
                    <li>Cobblestone: ~5 Stacks</li>
                    <li>Dark Oak Stairs & Slabs</li>
                    <li>Spruce Stairs & Slabs</li>
                    <li>Lanterns: ~30</li>
                    <li>Dark Oak Fences & Gates</li>
                    <li>(Add more specific materials as needed)</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

